@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000
@EmpresaId = 15

### Listar empresas
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/empresas
Accept: application/json

### Buscar empresa por ID
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/empresas/{{EmpresaId}}
Accept: application/json

### Criar empresa
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/empresas
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"nome": "Tech Solutions Ltda",
	"endereco": "Rua das Flores, 123",
	"telefone": "11 99999-9999"
}

### Atualizar empresa
PUT {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/empresas/{{EmpresaId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"nome": "Tech Solutions Ltda - Atualizada",
	"endereco": "Avenida Central, 500",
	"telefone": "11 98888-7777"
}

### Deletar empresa
DELETE {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/empresas/{{EmpresaId}}
Accept: application/json
